Thank you Debjani for a wonderful evening at the soft launch of Scrub Natural’s ‘Rainbow Soap’ especially on the onset of the PRIDE month. 

Had a mix of friends from the LGBTQIA++ Community as well as many straight allies!! 
I believe such events is how we can educate & talk about the LGBTQIA++ community & spread awareness!! 

Scrub Naturals doesn’t position themselves as just another beauty and wellness brand. The company believes that feeling good in our own skin is the ultimate form of self-care. Made with all-natural ingredients, the hand-crafted soap brand is on a mission to spread the message of self-love among everyone. The soaps are enriched with different essential oils, vitamins and other natural ingredients, which reduce numerous skin problems and also have aromatherapeutic benefits.

Through the event “Scrub Celebrates You”, the brand celebrated diversity, self-love and inclusion.

It was lovely to hear all the guests sharing stories of self-love. 

Thank you ALL my friends who were there in person as well as in spirit!! 

Makeup : @sumitsupu 
Saree : @anjushreesaree 
Kurta : @fabindiaofficial 

#celebratingyou #lovedbyscrub #rainbowsoap #pride #pridemonth #pride🌈 #straightally #friends #lgbtpride #loveislove

#chillvibes #girlgang #friendshipgoals

Friday evening spent well judging the Mr. / Mrs. / Miss. Kolkata Metropolis 2022 in association with @smpaiofficial . Thanks Mr. Srimani of Magnetite India for getting us on board for this!! Thanks Avijit for liaising this!! Had a wonderful time with my co judges @nickrampal & @falaque.rashidroy but it definitely was a herculean task for us, as all the contestants were at par with each other!! Was a pleasure meeting you @bobbychakraborty as always!! Congratulations to the winners & best wishes to ALL who participated!! @samrat.smpai was lovely meeting you after ages & loved your power packed performance!! ❤️❤️ Thanks & Kudos to ALL involved!! ❤️🙏
Post Covid it was indeed a nice feeling to see & be among a mass LIVE audience!! #pageant #judgementmodeon #openairevent #backtonormal #fingerscrossed🤞

Dola & I wanted to catch up with this bunch of girls we haven’t met for a long while!! Am glad we planned this Pre Poila Baisakh Lunch together and had a blast!! The Red & White Theme; Good Food & Great Adda - a perfect Wed afternoon!! Thanks to all who made it & we missed the few who got tied up!! @vanitabajoria loved the food & ambience!! Apologies for all the noise!! Finally my kind of gnocchi!  Definitely visiting soon!! And since Lopa Di’s Birthday month on, so we cut a cake for her too!! ❤️🎂 #girls  #poilaboishak #celebrations #redandwhite

Thanks @_veenukaur for a wonderful surprise pre birthday lunch for Lopa!! Loved the ambience & food at @theopus_hotel_kolkata !! Will visit soon!! Pleasure meeting you @sarandeepsingh1 !! 
Happy Birthday @lopamudramandalofficial in advance!! #jailopadi #prebirthdaycelebration #neverendingbirthdays #boutiquehotel

Had a wonderful time on the judge’s panel for ‘Dabur Amla Hair Oil - DQueen 2022’. Congratulations Tuhina, Roy Brothers & Team DQueen for a beautifully curated show!! My best wishes to all the contestants present & cheers to the winners!!

latestPosts.caption:
Thank You Binod Ji & @jayamisraofficial for a perfect culmination to the celebrations welcoming your grandson VIRAJ!! 
We all had a blast!! 
Titillating start by @mcsidofficial declaring me as the Kim Kardashian of Kolkata!! 🤣🤣🤣
Followed by the power house performance by @nakash_aziz making us all groove to his super hit numbers!!
The food spread was just too vast with literally every cuisine present!  Kudos to Team @itcroyalbengal for such delicious food & impeccable service!!
The highlight of the night was the after party with just a few of us happily stomping to the music being played by DJ @dippy.bindra !!

A fantastic weekend curated by Jaya herself in every aspect has given us all memories to cherish forever!! God Bless Viraj & Misra Family always!!

latestPosts.caption:
What a wonderful way to start off PRIDE month!!
The Lalit has been a pioneer in promoting inclusivity especially in the hospitality sector paving the path for many others to follow as well!! 
It was indeed an honour to Flag Off the onset of the Pride Month along with my dear friends Ruskshana & Suneha and Kamal with Team The Lalit Kolkata!! 
A big THANK YOU to Kamal, Arko & the entire Team of THE LALIT KOLKATA!!
Pride for me is everyday and just not one month but JUNE the world celebrates along with us so let the festivities begin!! ❤️🏳️‍🌈

#pride #lgbtqia #thelalitkolkata #prideparade #pridemonth2025

Thankyou @thelalitkolkata and @keshavsurifoundation for the incredible work that you do all through the year for the LGBTQIA community.
We were honoured to Flag off PRIDE Month celebrations with you and the Team. Happy Pride 🏳️‍🌈
Thankyou for your hospitality @iamkraza 
[Love is Love, Pure Love, Pride, Kolkata Diaries]
